                    <h3 class="heading">Reports & Logs – <span class="heading-rating">9/10</span></h3>
                    <p>Pumpic logs all essential data at once and sends it right to your Control Panel immediately. The app will let you monitor calls, SMS, contacts, calendar, emails, GPS location (including Geo-fences), photo and video files, visited websites, bookmarks, and applications. </p>
                    <p>Let’s take into that most dangers that our kids face in most cases come from the Internet. Fortunately, the application knows how to monitor social media (Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat) and online chats (Viber, WhatsApp, Skype, Kik). It means that cyberbullies and online predators will have no chances with Pumpic on your kid’s mobile phone or tablet. </p>
                    <h3 class="heading">Limits & Restrictions – <span class="heading-rating">10/10</span></h3>
                    <p>A good parental control application must let you not only monitor, but set restrictions as well. With Pumpic app on your command, you will be able to block apps and websites, limit application and the amount of SMS sent daily.</p>
                    <p>In addition, the app helps its users restrict phone numbers to prevent them from reaching your kid in future, and specify words and phrases your child will not see. Thus, you will be able to easily prevent your kid from bad language and threats.</p>
                    <h3 class="heading">Security & Management – <span class="heading-rating">10/10</span></h3>
                    <p>The process of monitoring your kids with Pumpic app is conducted via Control Panel. It is easy-to-use and requires no additional technical skills. There you can see all the data sent from your child’s device and control it remotely.</p>
                    <p>Moreover, the application allows remote wiping and locking. It will also let you know once a SIM card is changed. </p>
                    <h3 class="heading">Help & Support – <span class="heading-rating">10/10</span></h3>
                    <p>Pumpic provides its customers with all-round 24/7 support and assistance for free. If you have queries or question on the operation of the app, you can send your request anytime by choosing the most convenient way for you: an email, online form, or a live chat. You can also make a call and contact customer care representatives directly on the phone.</p>
					<p>The application is updated systematically. In addition, Pumpic keeps improving its tools and introduces new monitoring solution very often. That’s why by purchasing the app today you may be sure it will become even more advanced tomorrow. All innovations are available for all Pumpic clients.    </p>
                    <h3 class="heading">Conclusion – <span class="heading-rating">9.8/10</span></h3>
                    <p>Pumpic proved to be one of the best monitoring apps you can find online. It is trusted by more than 10,000 users worldwide. It includes all features you may need while taking care of your underage children. The app is a solution for safety and protection. Pumpic keeps your eyes open. </p>
                    
